<item>
            <title>[LU-12426] Add option to disable lock expansion on all requests</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12426</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It has come up several times recently that I wanted to disable lock expansion on all requests to explore possible shared file performance issues.&#160; This is not currently possible without modifying application codes, which is not always an option.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is primarily for testing, but it may increase performance in some situations.&#160; It would be nice to include this in a standard Lustre distribution so it&apos;s easy to test on real hardware.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
